<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٢٥٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6006">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يُوسُفَ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1906">ذَكْوَانَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2313">أَبِي سَعِيدٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«أَبْرِدُوا بِالصَّلَاةِ فَإِنَّ شِدَّةَ الْحَرِّ مِنْ فَيْحِ جَهَنَّمَ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>